===
Design a network for Accenture.com with 1750 agents, tm, admins. Use the 10.0.0.0/8 IP address space.
a 10.16.0.0/24
b 10.0.4.0/22
c 10.0.8.0/21
d 10.0.32.0/20

CSI
Convert:
   1750 = 11 bits
Subtract
   /32 - 11 = /21 = Network bits  (3rd, 8i)
Ipasok si i sa octet   ni 10.0.0.0

10.0.8.0 /21



====
Design a network for concentrix.com with 160 admin, 250 managers, 112 executive, 100 security agents. Use the 172.16.0.0/16 IP address space.
 172.16.8.0 /22
 172.16.16.0 /23
 172.16.4.0 /22
 172.16.2.0 /23

622 hosts

CSI
Convert
  622 = 10 bits
Subtract
  /32 - 10 = /22  (3rd, 4i)
Ipasok si i sa octet   ni 172.16.0.0/16
172.16.4.0 /22

===
Design and implement a network for foundever.com with 45 users. Use the 192.168.0.0/24 IP address space
CIA Method

CONVERT: 45 = 6 bits
SUBTRACT: /32 - 6 = /26 (4th, 64i)
INSERT(Ipasok):
Ipasok si i sa octet   ni 192.168.0.0/24
192.168.0.64/26

Network (foundever.com): 192.168.0.64/26
First Valid IP (+1 Network): 192.168.0.65
Last Valid IP (-1 Broadcast): 192.168.0.126
Last IP/Broadcast (-1 Not Network): 192.168.0.127

Not Network: 192.168.0.128/26

⦁	VLAN 26
⦁	Reserve First 10 IPs


config t
 vlan 26
  name _____.com
  exit
 int vlan 26
  ip add __.__.__.__  __.__.__.__
  ip ospf 1 area 0
  no shut
  exit
 ip dhcp excluded-add __.__.__.__  __.__.__.__
 ip dhcp pool _____.com
  network __.__.__.__  __.__.__.__
  default-router __.__.__.__
  domain-name _____.com
  dns-server 10.#$34T#.1.10
  option 150 ip 10.#$34T#.100.8
 int fa 0/7
  switchport voice vlan 26
  shut
  no shut
  end
show ip dhcp binding


===
Design and implement a network for etelecare.com with 178 users. Use the 192.168.0.0/24 IP address space
CIA Method
C: 178 = 8 bits
S: /32 - 8 = /24 (3rd, 1i)
I: 192.168.1.0/24

Network (etelecare.com): 192.168.1.0/24
First Valid IP (+1 Network): 192.168.1.1
Last Valid IP (-1 Broadcast): 192.168.1.254
Last IP/Broadcast (-1 Not Network): 192.168.1.255

Not Network: 192.168.2.0/24



561 - 582

!@CoreBABA
config t
 vlan 25
  name etelecare.com
  exit
 int vlan 25
  ip add 192.168.1.1 255.255.255.0
  ip ospf 1 area 0
  no shut
  exit
 ip dhcp excluded-add 192.168.1.1  192.168.1.100
 ip dhcp pool etelecare.com
  network 192.168.1.0  255.255.255.0
  default-router 192.168.1.1
  domain-name etelecare.com
  dns-server 10.12.1.10
  option 150 ip 10.12.100.8
 int fa 0/5
  switchport voice vlan 25
  shut
  no shut
  end
show ip dhcp binding


!@CoreBABA
conf t
 int fa0/5
  shut
  no shut
  end




