Subnet for 64 sites, using the network 10.0.0.0 /20
C: 64 = 6 bits
A: /20 + 6 = /26 (4th, 64i)
I:

Find the first 4 networks
10.0.0.0 /26 = First
10.0.0.64 /26
10.0.0.128 /26
10.0.0.192 /26
10.0.1.0 /26


